 <br/><a name='toc_1'></a>
<h1 class='doclevel'>1.Test Suite : mmir3559_BBT</h1>
<div><p>Se testează adăugarea unui produs.</p>
</div><a name="toc_tc29245"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P234-32: ECP_Valid_AddProduct&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Author:</span></td><td colspan="3">mmir3559</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Summary:</span><br /><p>Verificarea adăugării unui produs&nbsp;valid:</p>

<ul>
	<li>id: integer &gt; 0&nbsp;</li>
	<li>nume: string diferit de null</li>
	<li>pret: double &gt; 0</li>
	<li>categorie: enum, apartine {CLASSIC_COFFEE,&nbsp;MILK_COFFEE, SPECIAL_COFFEE, ICED_COFFEE,&nbsp;TEA,&nbsp;BUBBLE_TEA,&nbsp;JUICE,&nbsp;SMOOTHIE,&nbsp;ALL}</li>
	<li>tip: enum, apartine { BASIC, DAIRY, LACTOSE_FREE, WATER_BASED, PLANT_BASED, POWDER,&nbsp;ALL}</li>
</ul>
</td></tr><tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Preconditions:</span><br /><p>Produsul nu este deja adăugat</p>
</td></tr><tr><td><span class="label">#:</span></td><td><span class="label">Step actions:</span></td><td><span class="label">Expected Results:</span></td></tr><tr><td width="5">1</td><td><p>id = 8<br />
nume = &quot;cappuccino&quot;<br />
pret = 15<br />
categorie&nbsp; = MILK_COFFEE<br />
tip = DAIRY</p>
</td><td><p>Produsul este adăugat</p>
</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Execution type:</span></td><td colspan="3">Manual</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Estimated exec. duration (min):</span></td><td colspan="3"></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Importance:</span></td><td colspan="3">Medium</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"></td></tr><tr><td > name of the autotest class:</td><td  colspan = "3" ></td></tr>
<tr><td > name of the test method:</td><td  colspan = "3" ></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Requirements</span><td colspan="3">mmir3559_F01:  AdaugareProdus [Version : 1]<br /></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Keywords:</span></td><td colspan="3">&nbsp;None<br/></td></tr>
</table>
</div>
<a name="toc_tc29248"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P234-33: ECP_Invalid_AddProduct&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Author:</span></td><td colspan="3">mmir3559</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Summary:</span><br /><p>Verificarea adăugării unui produs invalid:</p>

<ul>
	<li>id: integer &gt; 0&nbsp;</li>
	<li>nume: string diferit de null</li>
	<li>pret: <strong>număr negativ</strong></li>
	<li>categorie: enum, apartine {CLASSIC_COFFEE,&nbsp;MILK_COFFEE, SPECIAL_COFFEE, ICED_COFFEE,&nbsp;TEA,&nbsp;BUBBLE_TEA,&nbsp;JUICE,&nbsp;SMOOTHIE,&nbsp;ALL}</li>
	<li>tip: enum, apartine { BASIC, DAIRY, LACTOSE_FREE, WATER_BASED, PLANT_BASED, POWDER,&nbsp;ALL}</li>
</ul>
</td></tr><tr><td><span class="label">#:</span></td><td><span class="label">Step actions:</span></td><td><span class="label">Expected Results:</span></td></tr><tr><td width="5">1</td><td><p>id = 18</p>

<p>nume = &quot;suc de portocale&quot;</p>

<p><strong>pret = -6</strong></p>

<p>categorie = JUICE</p>

<p>tip&nbsp; = PLANT_BASED</p>
</td><td><p>Se returnează un mesaj de eroare: prețul trebuie să fie un număr mai mare&nbsp;dec&acirc;t 0.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Execution type:</span></td><td colspan="3">Automated</td></tr>
